title: 03/25/2013 - The Church Of What's Happening Now #65
description:
Two great guests today. Television writer/producer and actor in Gangster Squad Mick Betancourt calls in. Also, boxer and story teller Vinny Curto calls in ahead of him joining Joey and Lee at the live Church at the Ice House.
